Survivors (2008-2010): A remake of the 1970s post-apocalyptic classic
Survivors is a two series (twelve episodes) post-apocalyptic TV drama broadcast on BBC One and the BBC HD channel between November 2008 and February 2010. It was broadcast on TV networks in the USA, Canada, Europe and beyond.
